      "message": "it calls your callback: https://pkg.go.dev/google.golang.org/api/support/bundler#NewBundler\nlooks like dispatching?\n\nI am going to use bundler in a non-LUCI RBE-specific repo approximately like this:\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/changes/88/2837288/1/client/rbe/cas/client.go#171",
